EmeraldView
version 0.2.0-b3 (third beta release)
http://yitznewton.org/emeraldview/

Changes from b2
* fixed bugs in installation script
* added support for tab-based HList classifier formatting
* completed implementation of mdoffset for correct display of classifer
  metadata where a node has multiple values for one field
* improved error redirecting and forwarding
* optimized Node building (necessary for building Node trees and using
  NodeTreeFormatter)
* fixed bug in parsing quoted search terms
* redesigned search snippet backend to use flat files instead of storing
  raw fulltext in the Lucene index
* various other bugfixes

